      "updated": 1781980138168,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Memento:\nMemento is the snapshot which we took everytime for each state.\n\n\nOriginator:\nObject which undergoes through state changes. Like in above example Ob1.\n\n\nCaretaker:\nHelps to store and manage Mementos/snapshots. It can have vector of Mementos.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Memento:\nMemento is the snapshot which we took everytime for each state.\n\n\nOriginator:\nObject which undergoes through state changes. Like in above example Ob1.\n\n\nCaretaker:\nHelps to store and manage Mementos/snapshots. It can have vector of Mementos.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
